<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-447] XMLLayout does not include marker name</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-447</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Log4j2 supports the notion of markers, but this is not represented by the XMLLayout.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example, using SerializedLayout with SocketAppender will send marker information, but using XMLLayout with SocketAppender will not.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be very helpful to have just the name of the leaf marker sent with the log event, not the corresponding marker hierarchy.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
